        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "cc3ac021-afd6-409c-be2b-df7e545f0e3a-23ab4b02-3f4f-43f6-a1d5-8d3b3c6f4737",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "クエン酸"
          },
          {
            "_key": "cc3ac021-afd6-409c-be2b-df7e545f0e3a-21fdb3a5-7e12-46dd-8cb7-994eb36d8554",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": ": 梅干しやレモンなど。疲労物質である乳酸の分解を促します。"
          }
        ],
        "level": 1,
